<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 03:16:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国大力推动人工智能，亚洲股市随美国股指期货下滑；美元公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2025-01-27/</link><description>周一，美国股指期货和中国以外的亚洲股市暴跌，投资者权衡了中国初创公司 DeepSeek 推出免费开源人工智能模型以与 OpenAI 的 ChatGPT 竞争的影响。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 02:59:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2025-01-27/</guid></item><item><title>因疫情中国阻止多国畜产品进口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-blocks-imports-livestock-products-many-countries-due-disease-outbreaks-2025-01-27/</link><description>海关总署周一表示，由于绵羊痘、山羊痘、口蹄疫等疾病的爆发，中国已禁止从许多国家进口牲畜及相关产品。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 02:42:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-blocks-imports-livestock-products-many-countries-due-disease-outbreaks-2025-01-27/</guid></item><item><title>2024年中国工业利润下降3.3% 连续第三年亏损</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-industrial-profits-fall-33-2024-third-year-red-2025-01-27/</link><description>这些数据凸显了政策制定者加大对面临关税威胁的经济体的支持的紧迫性。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 01:55:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-industrial-profits-fall-33-2024-third-year-red-2025-01-27/</guid></item><item><title>据《卫报》报道，中国外交部长将访问英国与拉米举行会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-foreign-minister-visit-uk-talks-with-lammy-guardian-reports-2025-01-26/</link><description>据《卫报》周日报道，中国外交部长王毅将于下个月访问英国，与英国外长戴维·拉米举行会谈。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 18:55:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-foreign-minister-visit-uk-talks-with-lammy-guardian-reports-2025-01-26/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普与多人讨论购买 TikTok，30 天内做出决定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/white-house-talks-have-oracle-us-investors-take-over-tiktok-npr-reports-2025-01-25/</link><description>根据正在谈判的交易，TikTok 的所有者字节跳动将保留该公司的股份，但数据收集和软件更新将由甲骨文监督。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 22:42:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/white-house-talks-have-oracle-us-investors-take-over-tiktok-npr-reports-2025-01-25/</guid></item><item><title>中央情报局 (CIA) 现在表示，COVID-19“更有可能”来自实验室</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/cia-now-says-covid-19-more-likely-have-come-lab-2025-01-25/</link><description>目前尚不清楚该机构在多大程度上收集了有关 COVID-19 起源的新情报，以及这些新证据是否用于制定最新评估。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 19:23:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/cia-now-says-covid-19-more-likely-have-come-lab-2025-01-25/</guid></item><item><title>上海用狗年宴庆祝农历新年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shanghai-celebrates-lunar-new-year-with-dogs-dinner-2025-01-25/</link><description>养乐多热情地咬了一口面前的鸡肉丝和生菜，然后舔了舔嘴唇。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 13:47:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shanghai-celebrates-lunar-new-year-with-dogs-dinner-2025-01-25/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾因中国“骚扰”而暂停南海调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-accuses-china-harassing-its-fisheries-boats-south-china-sea-2025-01-25/</link><description>菲律宾周六表示，在其两艘渔船面临中国海警和海军的“骚扰”和侵略行为后，该国已暂停在南海的一项科学调查。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 02:12:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-accuses-china-harassing-its-fisheries-boats-south-china-sea-2025-01-25/</guid></item><item><title>英国资深议员表示消费者和投资者希望了解中国棉花的真相</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/senior-uk-lawmaker-says-consumers-investors-want-truth-china-cotton-2025-01-24/</link><description>英国议会委员会主席周五表示，英国消费者和投资者希望了解英国在线快时尚零售商 Shein 是否销售来自中国新疆省棉花的产品的真相。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 16:50:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/senior-uk-lawmaker-says-consumers-investors-want-truth-china-cotton-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>王告诉卢比奥领导人已经确定了美中关系的基调和方向</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-top-diplomat-rubio-chinas-wang-speak-first-phone-call-china-says-2025-01-24/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅周五与美国新任国务卿马可·卢比奥通话，北京方面表示，他告诉这位著名的对华鹰派，美中关系的方向和基调已由两国领导人确定，他希望卢比奥发挥建设性作用为了两国人民的利益。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 16:36:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-top-diplomat-rubio-chinas-wang-speak-first-phone-call-china-says-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国称菲律宾向有争议环礁的军舰发送了物资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippines-sent-provisions-warship-disputed-atoll-2025-01-24/</link><description>中国海警表示，菲律宾周五派出一艘民用船只，向其“非法搁浅”在南海有争议环礁仁爱礁的军舰运送补给品。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 15:25:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippines-sent-provisions-warship-disputed-atoll-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>Shein告诉英国立法者，不允许在美国销售的产品中使用中国棉花</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-details-cotton-sourcing-policy-written-evidence-uk-lawmakers-2025-01-24/</link><description>在线快时尚零售商 Shein 周五表示，要求其合同制造商只能从经批准的地区（不包括中国）采购棉花，用于在其最大市场美国销售产品。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 11:31:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-details-cotton-sourcing-policy-written-evidence-uk-lawmakers-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>文本显示美国立法者寻求对香港进行人权制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-lawmakers-seek-rights-sanctions-over-hong-kong-text-shows-2025-01-24/</link><description>据路透社看到的法案文本，美国共和党和民主党议员将于周五提出一项法案，要求特朗普政府审查是否应因侵犯人权而对香港官员进行制裁。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 11:05:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-lawmakers-seek-rights-sanctions-over-hong-kong-text-shows-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>独家：律师称，赌博大亨因称自己为中国从事间谍活动而在泰国监狱中受到虐待</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/gambling-tycoon-abused-thai-jail-after-saying-he-spied-china-lawyers-say-2025-01-24/</link><description>一名被监禁的赌博大亨的律师告诉国际刑警组织，他们担心他的生命安全。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 10:54:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/gambling-tycoon-abused-thai-jail-after-saying-he-spied-china-lawyers-say-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>泰国和中国将设立打击诈骗电话网络协调中心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-china-set-up-coordination-centre-combat-scam-call-networks-2025-01-24/</link><description>泰国和中国将共同努力，打击泰国、缅甸和柬埔寨边境沿线快速增长的非法呼叫中心网络，这些呼叫中心的工作人员通常是被贩运的工人，旨在通过电话和网络诈骗来诈骗人们。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 10:41:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-china-set-up-coordination-centre-combat-scam-call-networks-2025-01-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>